Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:57.26,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0155,,{\fad(1000,0)\1c&HE4EEF7&\bord0\shad0\be1\fs54\pos(340,355)\fscy147}在蔚蓝宇宙『心跳不已』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢爆焰!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了  丈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈  你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈! 你振作点啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  奈奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来海边是去不成...了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.71,0:02:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想现在能安慰他的只有身为恋人的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个光看设计图就令人兴奋不已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说有三个新驾驶员要来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是这次送来的零G战模组
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒透了  这玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新来的最好是令人讨厌的臭男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨人厌的家伙比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是随时可能会阵亡的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是舰长命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说话！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要到达殖民地五月绿二号了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请立刻回到舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门开着啊  真是不小心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田先生的送到地球的行李…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠着海燕丈的牺牲  麦瑟克将军的挑战被击退了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是损失了驾驶员  自己也负伤的激钢人3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有办法再次复活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一分钟就可以看到殖民地了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:03:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次元歪曲防壁解除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备停泊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是机动战舰抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月绿二号  听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是五月绿二号  收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇… 好可爱的声音喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始停泊  准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  OK… 请放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地方向传来冲击波
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认受害状况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方是五月绿二号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防壁发动机第二区间附近  中度破损
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明刚才… 还在通讯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明刚才… 还在说话的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠  注意有没有生还者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上检查发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:05:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续确认周围的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候  万一遭到敌人的攻击…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还很小心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修补得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各员进入舰内警备状态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急通告所有成员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不明人物侵入本舰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员确认识别码的发信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰内补修班继续作业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他成员坚守岗位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  麦瑟克将军那混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢这样对我的激钢人3…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是出现了为处于劣势的我们助阵的好伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是龙崎铁也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有新的生力军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢人V
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从侧面确认机影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机有四架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防壁能用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:05:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发动机还要花十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五分钟内完成  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扩大机影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢气旋！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健  最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢爆焰！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了  丈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  丈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈  你振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  奈奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来海边是去不成..了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太过份了  丈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不住  奈奈子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  奈奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以去海边了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的激钢人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.85,0:07:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你看看我机械军团的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠着海燕丈的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦瑟克将军的挑战被击退了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是损失了驾驶员  自己也负伤的激钢人3
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是丈最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有办法再次复活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是最近才知道"激钢人3"的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越看越着迷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:43.73,BGS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,COSMIKE:   宇宙同人志即售会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我好想拿出旧本事出同人志参加COSMIKE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会突然掉下来？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是  失礼失礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你不会继续问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是说句"哪里哪里"嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS零G战模组
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我方的人  应该会传来识别讯号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道被挟持了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是忘记了识别密码
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么有自信？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢索上绑白色的记号…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拖吊的基本常识  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是指汽车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果木星蜥蜴会耍那种宝就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了  搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女..女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我要先洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问别人之前得先自我介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是御统百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本舰的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是昴凉子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS零G战模组只有四架？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机库的残骸中还剩下一架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没办法全部带出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外两位驾驶员怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能还活着  也可能挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是驾驶员天野光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇夫座B型  18岁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的东西是比萨边边的硬皮和稍微受潮的煎饼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有两人生还算不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.46,0:10:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随便把人杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着啊  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先打开工具箱看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空气真新鲜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你别关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不是鲭鱼罐头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙也是驾驶员  叫真木泉  以下省略
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在AESTIVALIS的检查补给之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托前往确认殖民地内的生还者以及回收剩下的一架
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  真是会使唤人的船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我要来的时候把战舰撞坏了一点点  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我把墙壁修补过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警戒状态解除
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  听说还有两个驾驶员在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.99,0:12:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有骗人咧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我本来是个厨师…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你完全不象驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我是厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当驾驶员也是临时的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.99,0:12:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始停泊  准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  OK… 请放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:12:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都不把别人的死当成一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙死了  也只有我一个人在难过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是我  有人死了的话也会很伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有小惠你会这么想而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我想以一个驾驶员的身份努力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也是漠不关心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是为那家伙和大家一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没有这种心情了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一个人挣扎着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人痛苦着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是搞不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并不是一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都会有想撒娇的时候嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来我只是在撒娇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试着以驾驶员的身份加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不快点闪开的话  会被踩扁的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力弹射器准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我这就上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我们的好消息咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力波充电
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴机去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:15:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来应该在我的鼓励下  让你一起出击才对的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  可是不要怨我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怪就怪那捉弄人的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又有一架出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会驾驶宇宙用的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟陆战用的驾驶舱没什么两样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本是一样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你了解这些基本吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可也是个驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  快回避
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴要乱来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有生物反应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的点的位置确认
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红烧猪肉（音同确认）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么冲进去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为来自抚子的能源传送要切断了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:54.49,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30\bord0\shad0\1c&HE4EEED&\be1}辅助电池所剩时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备用电池启动确认
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始潜行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红烧猪肉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到大珍珠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来可以开始回收作业了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也让我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没油了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和抚子之间有障碍物的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就没办法接收能源啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事是基本中的基本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我该怎么办才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要这么做！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太大意的话  可是会撞上抚子的力场的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔AESTIVALIS…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电脑被蜥蜴侵入了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我浪费能源
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总重量是对方比较重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用速度的差距冲到它怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近战的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外型这么笨重还如此敏捷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  凉子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.19,0:18:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是找上门来的架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然要打
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天保佑  老天保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双重攻击…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你中门大开了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  他朝抚子的方向去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里只有厨师一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河  干掉那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟以前的我已不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个撒娇的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是天河明人V
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙朝抚子的去了  抚子也会有危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也攻击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯  我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢爆焰！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了  太厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人  很帅喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你  明人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了  明人你很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦  我这是怎么了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦  一定是在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个可怕的恶梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然非常有现实感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.05,0:20:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只可能是在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(379,320)\fs70\fnArial Black\bord0\shad2\i1\be1\1c&HEEF5ED&\fsp-2\fscy123\fscx73\be1}FREEWIND
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.27,0:21:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香奔跑着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像命中注定一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:48.04,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}来自深邃遥远的宇宙空间的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.97,0:21:54.52,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}年轻人苦恼着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:02.05,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那是最后的边境
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.79,0:22:05.22,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人烦恼着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追寻着战斗的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.29,0:21:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯哭泣着  为了他那异常的纯情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  琉璃嘀咕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.53,0:21:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化为宇宙的巴士底狱的抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:21:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在点起了革命的烽火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战国魔神豪将军的首藤刚志
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自信满满地创造机械人动画的新世纪
